-- China Datang Gets Approval to Add 300 Megawatts at Yantan Hydropower Plant
-- Winnie Zhu
-- 2010-06-24T03:37:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/china-datang-gets-approval-to-add-300-megawatts-at-yantan-hydropower-plant.html

          
          
              China Datang Corp. won state
approval to expand its hydropower station and the company will
add two units with a capacity of 300 megawatts each at Yantan,
the National Development and Reform Commission said on its
website today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
